summary: At level 1 is just what you can have.
descriptionHtml:
[color=yellow][b]Description:[/b][/color]

Bored by huge and rich player homes, i have added a small tent near Riverwood.
A place to sleep, 3 minor potion to start your adventure and a personal chest. No more. (Barrel is set as respawn).
Have working map marker, you can fast travel to there.


Now featured on G.E.M.S. section 220!

[center][url=http://www.skyrimgems.com][img]http://i.imgur.com/hXQSy.png[/img][/url][/center]


Take a look at [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/38253/?tab=1&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fajax%2Fmoddescription%2F%3Fid%3D38253%26preview%3D&pUp=1]Starter tent 2[/url].


[color=yellow][b]Compatibilty:[/b][/color]

Everything, except mods that change same cell.
